   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Housing project for Congolese refugees in Kyaka II, Uganda</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="3">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">50 vulnerable refugees from D.R. Congo and their households. The beneficiaries will be People with Special Needs (PSN) and the project will engage refugees and host communities in shelter and livelihood construction activities.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The main goal is to contribute towards improving the living conditions and enhancing resilience of the most vulnerable PSN households in Kyaka II refugee settlement.</narrative>
